sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant App as App.svelte
  participant Runtime as AppRuntimeScreenContent
  participant Bootstrap as runtimeBootstrapController
  participant Bindings as runtimeBindingsController
  participant Preview as preview startup + controllers
  participant Modal as modal + interactive media

  User->>App: Open app
  App->>Runtime: mount controller + render runtime shell
  Runtime->>Bootstrap: mount()
  Bootstrap->>Bindings: create bound workflows/controllers
  Bindings->>Preview: init template, carousel, preload plan
  Preview-->>Runtime: startup progress + first interactive frame ready

  User->>Runtime: scroll / key navigation
  Runtime->>Preview: handleMenuScroll / shiftSection / shiftCarousel
  Preview-->>Runtime: focused section/item + background sync

  User->>Runtime: open dish modal
  Runtime->>Modal: openDish + prefetch detail media
  Modal-->>Runtime: modal interactive state

  User->>App: close / unload
  App->>Runtime: destroy()
  Runtime->>Bootstrap: destroy()
  Bootstrap->>Bindings: dispose timers/listeners/controllers
